INSERT INTO `blogs` VALUES (2,1,1,'CHASE','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 21px; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); line-height: 32px; margin: 3.2rem 0px; background: transparent; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: large;\">Why do employers prefer one candidate over others? Why do some people &ldquo;miss the right train&rdquo; in their career? Why do some employees become indispensable to their companies? In an attempt to find answers to these questions, team MBAtrek identified some core values which make certain individuals stand out- Character, Hope, Attitude, Skills &amp; Enthusiasm.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 21px; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); line-height: 32px; margin: 3.2rem 0px; background: transparent; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: large;\">Now, we were curious to determine which one of them is of utmost importance to an employer while recruiting. We did a short survey of a few professionals in leadership positions across multiple industries with 10- 25 years of experience. Our respondents have been hiring MBA graduates and engineers for years. The aim here was to ascertain which of these core values desired in a prospective employee is rated topmost by people at hiring positions.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 21px; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); line-height: 32px; margin: 3.2rem 0px; background: transparent; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: large;\">Our findings suggested that,</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 3.2rem 0px; background: transparent; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; outline: 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 2.4rem 0px 2.4rem 3.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: large;\">unanimously, Attitude and Character were rated the highest, followed by Hope &amp; enthusiasm, Knowledge, and Skill, in the same order.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 2.4rem 0px 2.4rem 3.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: large;\">Hence concluding, with the right attitude and strength in character, the skill and knowledge can be attained over time.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 2.4rem 0px 2.4rem 3.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: large;\">Moreover, skill and knowledge are developed and learned by everyone through formal education, but what makes one class-apart is the right Attitude and Character.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 21px; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); line-height: 32px; margin: 3.2rem 0px; background: transparent; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: large;\">We would like to personally thank all the people who took out time to participate and make this survey possible.</span></p>','Alok Srivastava','1387847327mba_logo.png','1916227829chase.png','2018-11-13 02:01:35','2018-11-22 04:15:48');
