oming batch of 2018 #MDI #Batchof2020.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 6px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: #1d2129; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">We loved the point of views and well thought through questions - absolute dream answering them.</span></p>',0),(13,1,'118744474IIMJ3.jpeg','56276914IIMJammu.jpeg','1321345056IIMJ2.jpeg','IIM Jammu','<p><span style=\"font-size: small; color: #000000;\"><strong>Indian Institute of Management Jammu</strong> thank you for having us over at the campus to present both our <strong>#Campus2Corporate</strong> and <strong>#InternGO</strong> series. Very impressed with how a young B-school is making rapid strides and focusing on building long-term capability especially in the students. We also had a great time interviewing students for summer internships and great to see the buzz on campus!</span></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>',6),(14,1,'1903142119IMG_20181027_173207.jpg','558401468IMG_20181027_173633.jpg','683761347IMG_20181027_173739.jpg','IIM Amritsar','<p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Fira Sans\', Ubuntu, Oxygen, \'Oxygen Sans\', Cantarell, \'Droid Sans\', \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Lucida Grande\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">An engaging session with <strong>Indian Institute of Management Amritsar 2018-2020 batch</strong> around <strong>How to Leverage the 2 Year MBA program</strong>. We had the opportunity to introduce them to our unique <strong>#InternGO program</strong>. Fantastic time also interviewing and shortlisting candidates for summer internships - great ideas, thoughts and it was nice to be challenged with an unconventional line of thinking!</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"e