INSERT INTO `faq` VALUES (1,1,'Who is a career adviser','The career adviser will act as a life-coach for the students and will help them in solving their issues in the best possible manner.'),(2,1,'Does MBAtrek provide Placement Guarantee','MBAtrek is not a placement agency so it cannot guarantee placements and it believes that no one can guarantee it but can prepare the students in such a way that they have an edge over others in the placement process'),(3,1,'How MBAtrek will help the students','MBAtrek will provide the students with a global curriculum, practical knowledge, problem-solving skills and thus making the student Industry Ready and Relevant. Our expert team will enable the students to become an effective and efficient Executive in no time.'),(4,1,'Can students visit the office for any queries faced during the program','Yes, MBAtrek is like a second home for the students and the students can anytime approach the company\'s office for any query.'),(5,1,'What is there for a student when the course is over','This course will create a lifelong impact in students life making them Industry Ready and Relevant.\r\nStudents can anytime after the course ask their queries and can be connected to our Industry Links.'),(6,1,'Does MBAtrek provide any certification for the program to the students','No, we believe that certification cannot prove your skills. It is the knowledge which student carries and the way he conducts. That know-how is what MBAtrek will teach students by practical application and not by certification.'),(8,1,'How MBAtrek will deliver its objective','There are series of simulation games, skill test, classes, practical examples, live projects, internships and much more that helps MBAtrek in delivering the objective.'),(9,1,'How is the performance of students measured and evaluated','Each student is allotted a career advisor which acts as a mentor for his query handling and evaluation apart from this there are tests, case studies, webinar etc that helps in evaluation of students performance.'),(11,1,'How can I get my Institute registered','You just need to register your institute in our website after which MBAtrek representative will give you a call for further process and detailing.'),(12,1,'Will MBAtrek help the Institutes in increasing placement record','MBAtrek is not a placement agency but yes we assure that there will be a positive impact on students thought and an increase in their skillset which will ultimately lead to an increase in placement record.'),(15,3,'What is \'One Point Contact\'\r\n','One point contact is a medium through which we can maintain our never ending relationship via mail. All the discussions, query handling, Institute discussions and fixing of meetings will be done through this contact \r\n'),(16,3,'Is there any cost involved in the process to be bore by me\r\n','No, we believe in improving employability and skills. Thus, MBAtrek will take all necessary steps to connect Industry with the Institutes and students \r\n'),(17,3,'How do I modify a vacancy already posted by me\r\n','You can anytime write to us and our team will modify all our posted vacancies-Internships, Live Projects, Placements etc.\r\n'),(18,3,'How can I keep a track on posting activity for my account\r\n','Our team will timely notify you on your posted applications through your \'One Point Contact\'\r\n'),(19,3,'How do I view the applications/responses received for the vacancy that I have posted\r\n','Our team will timely notify you on your posted applications through your \'One Point Contact\'\r\n'),(20,3,'Can I enter multiple jobs\r\n','Yes, one can enter as many jobs as they want\r\n'),(21,3,'Is there any time frame for posting any vacancy\r\n','No, there is no assigned time for your postings. However, availability of students depends on their respective Institute\r\n'),(22,3,'Is my profile visible to all\r\n','MBAtrek believes in high security standards and therefore your credentials will be visible to you and our team\r\n'),(23,3,'What if I have a problem with one of the candidate sent by your company(MBAtrek)\r\n','We will regularly monitor the hire to ensure better efficiency.But,if in case it happens,you can directly write to us \r\n'),(24,2,'What is \'One Point Contact\'','One point contact is a medium through which we can maintain our never ending relationship via email. All the discussions related to Institute, Students and Industry will be done through this contact.'),(25,2,'How to partner with MBAtrek','Register your Institute from our website after which one of our career advisors will get back to you for the further discussions.'),(26,2,'What is the course fees which Institute need to pay to partner with MBAtrek','All the discussion regarding the fees will be decided through one to one discussion since we customize our modules according to the need and requirement of the Institute.\r\n'),(27,2,'Will MBAtrek guarantee Placement of our students','MBAtrek does not guarantee placement but we assure you that our program is an end to end solution which will definitely make students Industry Ready & Relevant leading to an increase in placement trend.\r\nWe will definitely assist you on-campus in any placement support you require from us.\r\n'),(28,1,'Test','Test');
